OL,3,CWest Midlands Mayor blames Environment
OL,4,CAgency for house building delay
OL,6,FThe West Midlands Mayor has accused
OL,7,Fthe Environment Agency of hiding
OL,8,Fbehind "red tape and bureaucracy"
OL,9,Fwhile the region's biggest brownfield
OL,10,Fsite sits idle, six years after it was
OL,11,Fearmarked for much-needed housing.
OL,13,F630 homes were meant to be built at
OL,14,FFriar Park in Wednesbury, transforming
OL,15,Fthe former sewage works into a
OL,16,Fthriving new community.
OL,18,FHowever, progress has been at a
OL,19,Fstandstill, with the site failing to
OL,20,Fmeet the strict permit criteria
OL,21,Frequired by the Environment Agency.
