OL,3,CWest Midlands Mayor blames Environment
OL,4,CAgency for house building delay
OL,6,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV News
OL,7,FCentral West Midlands Mayor Richard
OL,8,FParker said: "I think the Environment
OL,9,FAgency has hidden behind the red tape
OL,10,Fand bureaucracy.
OL,12,F"I've had to get a grip of this issue
OL,13,Fand speak to them about the importance
OL,14,Fof this site.
OL,16,F"It is a perfect example of how red
OL,17,Ftape and bureaucracy stops us from
OL,18,Fattracting investment and getting
OL,19,Fhouses built in this region."
