OL,4,CAgency for house building delay
OL,6,FDespite the promise of new homes, the
OL,7,Fproject has hit a brick wall due to
OL,8,Fstringent regulations surrounding
OL,9,Fcontaminated land.
OL,11,FThe Environment Agency insists that a
OL,12,Fpermit can only be granted if five key
OL,13,Fconditions are met, one of which
OL,14,Frequires developers to prove that
OL,15,Fusing clean material instead of
OL,16,Fremediated waste would offer a
OL,17,Ffinancial advantage.
OL,19,FFriar Park doesn't tick any of the
OL,20,Fnecessary boxes, meaning that, for
OL,21,Fnow, the project remains in limbo.
