OL,3,CWest Midlands Mayor blames Environment
OL,4,CAgency for house building delay
OL,6,FHe insists the system requires reform,
OL,7,Fas excessive red tape is slowing down
OL,8,Fessential development at a time when
OL,9,Fthe Midlands is crying out for new
OL,10,Fhomes.
OL,12,FWith housing demand at an all-time
OL,13,Fhigh, the pressure is mounting on both
OL,14,Flocal and national governments to
OL,15,Fbreak the deadlock and get projects
OL,16,Flike Friar Park back on track.
